name: Astro Boy

description:

name: Alaskan Blackberry
description:
Not to be confused with the similarly named "Blackberry," Alaskan Blackberry is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through a cross of the delicious Obama Kush X (Blackberry X Goji OG) strains. With parents like these, you know you're in for one tasty smoke with this baby. Alaskan Blackberry has a super sweet fruity berry flavor with a rich hint of diesel and grapes as you exhale.
